P_1,

00:11:03.750 --> 00:11:07.899
but that's equal to (1 -
d_1) times (1 -

00:11:07.899 --> 00:11:11.120
d_2( times
P_1,

00:11:11.120 --> 00:11:18.700
which is (1 - d_3)
times P_3,

00:11:18.700 --> 00:11:22.178
